quote.summary: Fire Rock Holdings Limited is a Singapore-based investment holding company. The Company is a game developer, publisher, and operator, which is engaged in the development and operation of self-developed browser and mobile games and provision of software licensing. The Company's segments include Game and software development and publishing; Game operation and publishing. The Game operation and publishing segment is engaged in the mobile game operation and/or publishing. The Company and its subsidiaries are principally engaged in the development of mobile games, including game design, programming and graphics, and computer software related to game operation. The Company assists third parties in promoting game-related business and provides intellectual property rights licensing services to businesses. The Company also self-operates its self-developed game products in overseas markets. Its subsidiaries include Wisdom Pure International Limited and Fire Rock International Limited.
